```

Light theme overrides all modal classes via `:root:not([data-theme="dark"])` selectors — see Section 13 for the color mapping.

### Diff Rendering Classes

```css
.diff-view    { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; }

/* Unified diff */
